column2: WHAT ARE THE CONDITIONS OF EMPLOYMENT OF STUDENTS
column5:
#Newline
  1. The student should study at his own expense.
    2. #Newline
  2. The average should not be less than 2 points.
    3. #Newline
  3. He must not have been subject to any disciplinary sanction.
    4. #Newline
